SUMMARY:SpongeBob the Musical\, Youth Edition
DESCRIPTION:SpongeBob the Musical\, Youth Edition in Davis – May 2 through May 24\, 2026\nSchool Matinees: May 5\, 2026; 9:15am and noon \nUnderwritten by Dr. Jennifer & Scott Goldman\, DDS\n  \nPlunge into this stunning dynamic stage show! When the citizens of Bikini Bottom discover that a volcano will soon erupt and destroy their humble home\, SpongeBob and his friends must come together to save the fate of their undersea world. With lives hanging in the balance and all hope lost\, a most unexpected hero rises up. The power of optimism really can save the world! \nAges 5 and up \n  \nDirected by Morgan Bartoe\nMusical direction by Montana Monce
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/spongebob-the-musical-youth-edition/2026-05-09/
LOCATION:Davis Musical Theatre Company (DMTC)\, The Jean Henderson Performing Arts Center\, 607 Pena Drive\, Davis
ORGANIZER;CN="Davis Musical Theatre Company (DMTC)":MAILTO:info@dmtc.org
END:VEVENT
