SUMMARY:Mother’s Day Brunch at The HIVE
DESCRIPTION:An over the top Mother’s Day brunch for the entire family. Celebrate surrounded by loved ones and the natural beauty of our pollinator habitat with live music by local Brazilian Samba duo\, Boca do Rio. Enjoy an elaborate seasonal buffet\, craft mead pairings\, meadmosas and more. \nTickets at https://thehivewoodland.com/event/mothers-day-brunch-2/
