SUMMARY:Mother's Day Brunch at Great Bear Vineyards
DESCRIPTION:Mother’s Day Brunch at Great Bear Vineyards in Davis Sunday\, May 10 | 10:30 am – 12:30 pm$35 per person | $20 for kids ages 3–10\nTreat Mom to a morning she’ll truly savor  Join us at Great Bear Vineyards for a joyful Mother’s Day Brunch surrounded by spring blooms\, vineyard views\, and live music. Settle in with a glass of sparkling wine or a mimosa.\n Brunch Menu Includes:• Seasonal fresh fruit bowl• Cranberry apple quinoa salad• Mediterranean orzo pasta salad• Breakfast potatoes• Vegetable quiche• Ham\, cheese & potato quiche• French toast• Bacon• Assorted breakfast breads & pastries\n Optional Additions:• Glass of sparkling wine or mimosa — $10• Bottle of Chardonnay\, Rosé\, or Red Blend (The Duet)• Bottle of Sparkling Rosé — $57.50\nWhether you’re celebrating Mom\, Grandma\, or all the incredible women in your life\, this is an easygoing\, delicious way to say thank you—with great food\, beautiful music\, and plenty of time to linger.\n Space is limited—reserve your spot and make this Mother’s Day one to remember!
URL:https://visityolo.com/event/mothers-day-brunch-at-great-bear-vineyards-2/
LOCATION:Great Bear Vineyards\, Great Bear Vineyards  24800 Co Rd 101A\, Davis\, CA 95616
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visityolo.com/wp-content/uploads/Great-Bear-Vineyards_23GBV-drone-scaled.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Great Bear Vineyards":MAILTO:greatbearvineyards@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
